    "title": "Azure与OpenAI联手，为政府机构提供人工智能解决方案",
    "url": "https://www.infoq.cn/article/u6hQhlyfAGp1k8MLyErM",
    "summary": "<p>微软将继续优先开发符合美国监管标准的云服务，并满足政府对安全性和合规性的要求。他们推出了通过微软<a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/products/cognitive-services/openai-service/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">Azure OpenAI Service</a>\"集成生成式AI能力的工具，旨在提高政府机构的效率、生产力和数据洞察力。</p><p></p><p>微软意识到政府机构不仅需要处理敏感数据，而且有严格的安全性需求。为了解决这个问题，微软推出了微软<a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/explore/global-infrastructure/government/get-started/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">Azure Government</a>\"云解决方案，它遵循严格的安全和合规标准，确保政府的敏感数据得到保护。</p><p></p><p>支持<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Generative_artificial_intelligence?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">生成式AI</a>\"工具的大型语言模型一般只能在商业云中使用，但微软已经设计出了一个新的架构，让政府机构能够在Azure Government中安全地访问这些语言模型。这确保了用户能够获得政府云操作所需的安全性。</p><p></p><p>Azure Government用户，包括美国联邦、州和地方政府机构及其合作伙伴，现在可以使用微软Azure OpenAI Service了。专门构建和优化的AI基础设施现在可以访问由OpenAI开发的高级生成模型，如<a href=\"https://openai.com/gpt-4?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">GPT-4</a>\"、<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GPT-3?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">GPT-3</a>\"和Embeddings。这些模型可用于完成特定的任务，包括内容生成、摘要、语义搜索和自然语言到代码的翻译。</p><p></p><p>用户可以通过<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cognitive-services/openai/reference?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">REST API</a>\"、<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cognitive-services/openai/quickstart?tabs=command-line&amp;pivots=programming-language-python&amp;accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">Python SDK</a>\"或<a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/blog/build-next-generation-ai-powered-applications-on-microsoft-azure/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">Azure AI Studio</a>\"的基于Web的接口来访问Azure OpenAI Service。借助Azure OpenAI Service，政府用户和合作伙伴可以扩展和运营先进的AI模型和算法。开发人员可以利用预训练的GPT模型，以最小的工作量快速构建和部署支持AI的应用程序。</p><p></p><p>Azure Government的网络连接与商业Azure网络对等，为互联网和微软企业网络提供路由和传输功能。Azure Government采用额外的保护和通信功能来限制其暴露的表面积。Azure区域内或区域之间的所有Azure流量都使用<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Advanced_Encryption_Standard?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">AES-128分组密码</a>\"进行加密，并保留在微软全球网络骨干网内，不进入公共互联网。</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://static001.geekbang.org/infoq/d4/d45b9c4332bb4ba6e24ffc107e459901.webp\" /></p><p></p><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/blog/unlock-new-insights-with-azure-openai-service-for-government/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/blog/unlock-new-insights-with-azure-openai-service-for-government/</a>\"</p><p></p><p>Azure OpenAI Service提供的能力能够极大地使政府用户受益，包括加速内容生成、简化内容摘要、优化语义搜索和简化代码生成。政府机构可以通过自动化响应、生成摘要、增强信息发现和使用自然语言查询来改进其运营效率和决策过程。</p><p></p><p>此外，微软高级区域销售总监兼网络安全业务主管<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/aydina/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">Aydin Aslaner</a>\"在领英上的一篇<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/feed/update/urn:li:share:7044917966722768896/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">帖子</a>\"中列举了一些政府机构的例子：</p><p></p><p>在医疗保健方面：GPT-4可以帮助对患者进行诊断，回答常见的问题，并根据医疗记录和症状提供个性化建议。在教育方面：GPT-4可以协助进行学生咨询、职业指导和为个性化学习生成内容。在司法方面：GPT-4可以帮助进行法律研究、文件分析和案件管理，提高效率和准确性。</p><p></p><p>对于满足特定标准和用例的用户，微软允许其修改<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/azure/cognitive-services/openai/concepts/content-filter?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">Azure OpenAI内容管理功能</a>\"，包括数据记录。如果获得批准，则不会在Azure商业版中存储与已配置的Azure订阅相关的任何提示词。</p><p></p><p>Azure Government保持了严格的合规性标准，确保保护数据、隐私和安全性，并提供修改内容过滤器和数据记录的<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/nl-nl/legal/cognitive-services/openai/limited-access?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">审批流程</a>\"。用户通过完成这个<a href=\"https://customervoice.microsoft.com/Pages/ResponsePage.aspx?id=v4j5cvGGr0GRqy180BHbR7en2Ais5pxKtso_Pz4b1_xURE01NDY1OUhBRzQ3MkQxMUhZSE1ZUlJKTiQlQCN0PWcu&amp;accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">过程</a>\"可以确保Azure商业版中不存在日志数据。微软的Azure OpenAI Service数据、隐私和安全性网站提供了修改数据记录设置的详细说明和示例。</p><p></p><p>最后，关于Azure OpenAI Service的更多细节可以在<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cognitive-services/openai/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">文档登录页面</a>\"和<a href=\"https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cognitive-services/openai/faq?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">FAQ</a>\"中找到。</p><p></p><p></p><p>原文链接：</p><p><a href=\"https://www.infoq.com/news/2023/06/azure-openai-government-agencies/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2ODkzMDE2NTEsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoib1k2elBCWllObGdjSnBSMiIsImlhdCI6MTY4OTMwMTM1MSwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.gd47RYULLf-bHqnBLerKOLf18ijXRP9Fun-I9FGm7kA\">https://www.infoq.com/news/2023/06/azure-openai-government-agencies/</a>\"</p>",
